      "type": "custom-html",
      "settings": {
        "code": "<div class=\"t4s-text-center\" style=\"background-color: #252525;color: #fff;\">\n<div class=\"footer-seo\">\n  <h2>NG EarSafe - The Future of Open-Ear Audio Technology</h2>\n  <p><strong>NGearSafe</strong> is revolutionizing the way people experience audio with its innovative <strong>open-ear headphones</strong>. Unlike traditional earbuds that block your ears, our advanced <strong>bone conduction and air conduction technology</strong> delivers high-quality sound while keeping you aware of your surroundings. Whether you are a fitness enthusiast, commuter, or professional, NGearSafe offers an unparalleled listening experience that prioritizes both safety and comfort.\n    </p>\n  <h3>Why Choose NG EarSafe Open-Ear Headphones?</h3>\n  <p>\n    Traditional in-ear headphones can cause discomfort and potential hearing damage due to prolonged use. NG EarSafe’s unique \n    open-ear design eliminates these concerns, ensuring you enjoy music, calls, and podcasts without blocking external sounds. \n    This makes it an ideal choice for runners, cyclists, office workers, and gamers who need a balance between entertainment \n    and situational awareness.\n  </p>\n  <h3>Unmatched Comfort and Cutting-Edge Features</h3>\n  <p>\n    Designed with an ultra-lightweight and ergonomic build, NG EarSafe headphones provide a secure and comfortable fit for all-day wear. \n    Our latest models offer <strong>Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity</strong> for seamless pairing, <strong>long battery life</strong> for extended \n    usage, and an <strong>IPX waterproof rating</strong> for protection against sweat and splashes. The built-in noise-canceling microphone \n    ensures crystal-clear calls, making it perfect for professionals who require hands-free communication.\n  </p>\n  <h3>The Ideal Choice for an Active Lifestyle</h3>\n  <p>\n    Whether you're working out, traveling, or working from home, NG EarSafe enhances your lifestyle with its innovative sound delivery system. \n    Stay aware of your environment while enjoying premium audio quality. Say goodbye to ear fatigue and embrace a new way of listening with \n    the most advanced <strong>open-ear headphones</strong> on the market.\n  </p>\n  <p>At <strong>NG EarSafe</strong>, we offer a diverse selection of <strong>open-ear headphones</strong> tailored to various lifestyles and needs. Our collection includes the lightweight <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/open-ear-wireless-headphones-ng-ear-safe-lite\">NG EarSafe Lite Open Ear Wireless Headphones</a></strong> for everyday use, the professional-grade <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/noise-cancelling-open-ear-headphones-with-mic-ng-ear-safe-comm-2-0\">NG EarSafe Comm Open Ear Headphones</a></strong> with a noise-canceling boom mic, and the advanced <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/open-ear-bone-conduction-headphones-ng-ear-safe-pro-swimming\">NG EarSafe Pro Open Ear Bone Conduction Headphones</a></strong> for high-quality sound transmission. Additionally, we provide the versatile <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/collections/open-ear-headphones\">NG EarSafe Open Ear Bluetooth Headphones</a></strong>, the innovative <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/open-ear-earbuds-wireless-ng-ear-safe-buds\">NG EarSafe OpenBuds Air Conduction Open Ear Earbuds</a></strong>, and the compact <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/products/open-ear-bone-conduction-headphones-ng-ear-safe-pro-mini\">NG EarSafe Pro Mini Open Ear Bone Conduction Headphones</a></strong>. Each product is designed to deliver superior audio quality while keeping you connected to your environment, ensuring safety and comfort during use. <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/collections/open-ear-headphones\">Explore our full range</a></strong> today to find the perfect open-ear headphones that suit your lifestyle.</p>\n  <h3>Experience the NG EarSafe Difference Today</h3>\n  <p>\n    Join thousands of satisfied customers who have upgraded their listening experience with NG EarSafe. Explore our range of \n    cutting-edge audio solutions and find the perfect pair of <strong>open-ear headphones</strong> for your needs. \n    <strong><a href=\"https://ngearsafe.com/\">Shop Now</a></strong> and enjoy exclusive offers, fast shipping, and a 100% satisfaction guarantee!\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.footer-seo{padding:40px 20px;color:#ddd;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;text-align:left}\n.footer-seo h2,.footer-seo h3{color:#fff;margin-bottom:15px;font-size:16px}\n.footer-seo p{color:#ccc;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:15px}\n.footer-seo ul{list-style:none;padding-left:0}\n.footer-seo ul li{margin-bottom:10px;color:#ddd;font-size:16px}\n.footer-seo a{color:#56cfe1 font-weight: bold;text-decoration:none;transition:.3s ease-in-out}\n.footer-seo a:hover{text-decoration:underline;color:#ff4672}\n@media (max-width:768px){\n.footer-seo{padding:30px 15px;}\n.footer-seo ul li{padding-left:0;background:0 0}\n}\n</style>\n</div>",
